          "segment_text": "Once a horse met an elephant, and then they saw a ball in a pool"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg2",
          "segment_text": " The horse tried to swim and get the ball, and then the elephant gave him the ball"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg3",
          "segment_text": " The horse was wet, and the elephant was holding the ball"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "story_id": "2",
      "start_time": "2023-05-07T09:05:00",
      "end_time": "2023-05-07T09:08:00",
      "segments": [
        {
          "segment_id": "sg1",
          "segment_text": "Once a horse saw that I just talked about, but the ball was not in there"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg2",
          "segment_text": " The elephant wanted to go in, but he hurt his knee cap"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg3",
          "segment_text": " The horse helped him, and then there was another elephant who was a lifeguard"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg4",
          "segment_text": " They are doing something"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg5",
          "segment_text": " I think they are battling"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg6",
          "segment_text": " Then they sat on the bench, and the lifeguard was mad"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "story_id": "3",
      "start_time": "2023-05-07T09:10:00",
      "end_time": "2023-05-07T09:12:30",
      "segments": [
        {
          "segment_id": "sg1",
          "segment_text": "Once, the horse and the elephant were happy near the swimming pool"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg2",
          "segment_text": " The horse had an airplane to play with, which had something coming down at the bottom"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg3",
          "segment_text": " The elephant tried it, and the horse was mad"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg4",
          "segment_text": " The lifeguard tried to get it but he could not"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg5",
          "segment_text": " The horse cried, and then an elephant with a net came and caught it"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg6",
          "segment_text": " She gave it back to the horse, and then the horse loved it"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "story_id": "4",
      "start_time": "2023-05-07T09:15:00",
      "end_time": "2023-05-07T09:17:00",
      "segments": [
        {
          "segment_id": "sg1",
          "segment_text": "Once two rabbits made a sandcastle."
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg2",
          "segment_text": " It was a great one. "
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg3",
          "segment_text": " One took some sand from a pail, and the other one took some sand, and he dumped it on the castle"
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg4",
          "segment_text": " Part of it stayed the way it was, but the rest turned into just a lump. "
        },
        {
          "segment_id": "sg5",
          "segment_text": "The end."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
